cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.AI, cs.IT

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on predicting user traffic in cellular networks.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper employs standard machine learning and statistical learning time series prediction methods.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is a possible category as the paper deals with network traffic classification and prediction of traffic bursts.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques for prediction and classification.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with analyzing and predicting network traffic data.
